*welcome2l-3.04 (23 Aug 2003)

  23 Aug 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> welcome2l-3.04.ebuild,
  files/welcome2l-3.04-gentoo.patch, files/welcome2l.initscript:
  moved from Welcome2L to welcome2l (proper nomenclature).  Also, changed
  the initscript to "need local" instead of "after *" -- thanks to sorcerer
  in #gentoo for pointing out the failure with that.

*Welcome2L-3.04 (07 Nov 2002)

